data.description: Gorgeous brick cape cod on a large corner lot with exceptional curb appeal. Main floor primary en suite with walk in closet, double vanity, soaking tub and separate shower.  Living room features a gas fireplace, cathedral ceiling and neutral carpet. Wood floors flow through dining room to kitchen, hall and powder room. Loft with closet could easily be made into a fourth bedroom. Turn the second floor bonus room into a cozy remote office or craft room. This home also features a first floor laundry, full basement, all new HVAC and water heater, attached side entry garage, patio and so much more.
